      "title_fr": "New Mythical Pokémon Pecharunt officially revealed",
      "summary_fr": "<p>A new trailer has been released by The Pokémon Company, which officially announces the mythical Pokémon, <strong><a href=\"https://pokemondb.net/pokedex/pecharunt\">Pecharunt</a></strong>. It's Poison/Ghost and has a new ability <a href=\"https://pokemondb.net/ability/poison-puppeteer\">Poison Puppeteer</a> which causes poisoned Pokémon to also become confused.</p>\n\n<p>Pecharunt is available during the epilogue of the Scarlet/Violet expansion pass. An additional video telling the story of Pecharunt's history was also released, see below.</p>",
