      "title_fr": "“Pitch Black” Preorders Now Live on Pokemon Center!",
      "summary_fr": "<div class=\"bbWrapper\"><blockquote class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--expandable bbCodeBlock--quote js-expandWatch\">\n\t\n\t<div class=\"bbCodeBlock-content\">\n\t\t\n\t\t<div class=\"bbCodeBlock-expandContent js-expandContent \">\n\t\t\t<a class=\"link link--internal\" href=\"https://www.pokebeach.com/news/2026/04/Pitch-Black-Pokemon-Center-Elite-Trainer-Box-Front.jpg\"><img class=\"bbImage \" height=\"\" src=\"https://www.pokebeach.com/news/2026/04/Pitch-Black-Pokemon-Center-Elite-Trainer-Box-Front-200x191.jpg\" width=\"\" /></a>Preorders for select <a class=\"link link--internal\" href=\"https://www.pokebeach.com/2026/04/pitch-black-tcg-set-and-product-lineup-officially-revealed\">Pitch Black</a> products are now available on the Pokemon Center:<br />\n<br />\n<a class=\"link link--external\" href=\"https://www.pokemoncenter.com/product/10-10416-112\" rel=\"nofollow ugc noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Elite Trainer Box</a><br />\n<a class=\"link link--external\" href=\"https://www.pokemoncenter.com/product/10-10422-109\" rel=\"nofollow ugc noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Booster Bundle</a><br />\n<a class=\"link link--external\" href=\"https://www.pokemoncenter.com/product/10-10425-120\" rel=\"nofollow ugc noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Booster Box</a><br />\n<br />\nThe set officially releases on July 17th. Thus, preorders opened 37 days before; for Chaos Rising, it was 39 days before. It seems the Pokemon Center&#039;s new preorder window is a little over a month before a set releases.",
      "category": "nouveaux_sets",
